<h3>What do I do if I don’t know all the facts about my criminal record?</h3>
<p>If you do not know the exact charge, date, or outcome of your case, you can search your adult criminal record (including traffic violations) at the State of Maryland Judiciary Case Search. <a href="http://casesearch.courts.state.md.us/inquiry/inquiry-index.jsp" target="_blank">Click here</a> to access this site. (Disclaimer: if your case was recently resolved, or currently pending, this site might not be updated with that information)</p>

